Package net.markenwerk.utils.json.common.handler.replay.events

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonEvent
    A JsonEvent represents an event that has been reported to a RecordingJsonHandler (i.e a call to the corresponding callback method).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayBeginJsonEvent
    An ArrayBeginJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onArrayBegin().
    ArrayEndJsonEvent
    An ArrayEndJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onArrayEnd().
    BooleanJsonEvent
    A BooleanJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onBoolean(boolean).
    DocumentBeginJsonEvent
    A DocumentBeginJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onDocumentBegin().
    DocumentEndJsonEvent
    A DocumentEndJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onDocumentEnd().
    DoubleJsonEvent
    A DoubleJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onDouble(double).
    LongJsonEvent
    A LongJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onLong(long).
    NameJsonEvent
    A NameJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onName(String).
    NextJsonEvent
    A NextJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onNext().
    NullJsonEvent
    A NullJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onNull().
    ObjectBeginJsonEvent
    A ObjectBeginJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onObjectBegin().
    ObjectEndJsonEvent
    A ObjectEndJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onObjectEnd().
    StringJsonEvent
    A StringJsonEvent is a JsonEvent that represents a call to JsonHandler.onString(String).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    JsonEventType
    A JsonEventType describes the type of a JsonEvent.
